   "end": "9.480", 
   "id": "s000001", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Der Verweis auf die US-Sammelklage ist ungef\u00e4hr so schlagkr\u00e4ftig wie das Vertr\u00f6sten auf Softwarenachr\u00fcstungen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "9.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "11.000", 
   "id": "s000002", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wenn Sie sich einmal damit befassen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "11.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "13.120", 
   "id": "s000003", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "was die US-Sammelklage ausmacht, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "13.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "14.400", 
   "id": "s000004", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dann werden Sie merken, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "14.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "17.160", 
   "id": "s000005", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass nichts davon in diesem Gesetzentwurf enthalten ist. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "17.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "19.120", 
   "id": "s000006", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wenn Sie damit ablehnen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "19.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "24.080", 
   "id": "s000007", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "den Verbraucherinnen und Verbrauchern und den Unternehmen ein st\u00e4rkeres Recht vor Gericht zuzubilligen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "24.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "26.520", 
   "id": "s000008", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dann sagen Sie einfach nicht die Wahrheit."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "26.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "30.600", 
   "id": "s000009", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Die Sammelklage in den USA erm\u00f6glicht nicht nur, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "30.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "32.360", 
   "id": "s000010", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "den tats\u00e4chlichen Schaden einzuklagen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "32.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "33.560", 
   "id": "s000011", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wie in unserem Gesetzentwurf, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "33.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "33.880", 
   "id": "s000012", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "sondern auch, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "33.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "35.400", 
   "id": "s000013", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Strafsch\u00e4den einzuklagen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "35.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "38.120", 
   "id": "s000014", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Niemand will das hier einf\u00fchren. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "38.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "41.680", 
   "id": "s000015", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Die Amerikaner haben einen anderen Grundsatz als wir: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "41.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "44.800", 
   "id": "s000016", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Nicht der Verlierer tr\u00e4gt die Kosten des Verfahrens, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "44.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "47.120", 
   "id": "s000017", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "sondern dort gibt es Erfolgshonorare. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "47.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "49.560", 
   "id": "s000018", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Niemand will das hier einf\u00fchren."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "49.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "56.960", 
   "id": "s000019", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Auch die Anforderungen an die Darlegung des Schadensersatzes und die tats\u00e4chlichen Darlegungen sind in den USA niedriger. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "56.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "58.960", 
   "id": "s000020", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Niemand will das hier einf\u00fchren. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "58.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "60.400", 
   "id": "s000021", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das ist ein Popanz."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "60.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "62.120", 
   "id": "s000022", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Am allerschlimmsten finde ich, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "62.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "65.160", 
   "id": "s000023", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass Sie von einer Klageindustrie reden, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "65.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "68.000", 
   "id": "s000024", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wo es um ganz normale Leute geht, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "68.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "69.640", 
   "id": "s000025", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die nicht so viel Geld, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "69.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "73.840", 
   "id": "s000026", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "vergleichbare Rechtsabteilungen oder gro\u00dfe Kanzleien zur Verf\u00fcgung haben. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "73.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "76.480", 
   "id": "s000027", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Die diskreditieren Sie als Klageindustrie. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "76.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "79.880", 
   "id": "s000028", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Dabei sch\u00fctzen Sie die Klageabwehrindustrie."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "79.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "85.600", 
   "id": "s000029", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Herr Kollege Steineke, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "85.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "88.000", 
   "id": "s000030", 
